text: Vuk Malidžan (, born January 14, 1988) is a Serbian professional basketball player for Dunav of the Basketball League of Serbia. == Professional career == Malidžan played for the Superfund BP (Second League of Serbia), and for OKK Beograd and Dunav Stari Banovci of Basketball League of Serbia. He was selected as the First League MVP in 2014–15 season. Prior to 2017–18 season, he signed for Mladost Zemun.
